text:
Erm, im not sure if you, or anyone any of you are connected to will read this. I assume it could be possible, eventually; offen I've noticed an idea ive shared, even just in person to a stranger, to have become a bit more widespread - makes sense, a lot of people wont rexognize it happening with them, but well, people talk. 

Anyway, I kinda believe the following. But i acknowledge it could be delusion.
Like the lyrics (which im not sure are lyrics or not; if not, well they're great):
"Is it my imagination,
Is it just delusion."

I believe i may have had sent to myself, glimpses of memories, from my unconscious. Working with them, & questioning-ish my unconscious, ive managed to form an accurate-ish/vague/general series of events as well as a list; as I felt, from behind a place where i can put on a front; i felt feelings that were signs that they occured; because they were what id feel had they occured; & i felt them from deeper than a place i could delude or decieve at all.

I figured id comment this on the videos of some of those who wanted to, err shall we say, dance with myself, the most, and, so probably did.

I guess Id like to say, if it aint delusion, or just my imagination, after all.

I feel i love you.
I actually ended up met with my innocence taken advantage of later, by people whom i can only assume knew and must've acted on their jelousy or hate or both; they could've just tried to do some personal growth or something, for the purpose of a similar err "situation", if they really wanted it that badly; ive come to know just what fruits personal growth, & the pursuit of more accurate knowledge, can bring-irrespective of what reason drives you at first.
But i got better. Partly on my part; and partly because of others; i think it is really our culture & society; on levels unconscious, we together are evolving - i think more spiritually. 
Anyway, i hope each of you, and you're err "group" or something, fared well; and if not, then that you too are getting better - you must practice patience with each other, as one challenge can be the burden of darkness; im sure i could help somehow. In fact i know some effective healing mantras, I'll put them below. It'd be great if they got around too.
Also, some final words to end this message i suppose. 
Hmm. I feel i miss you, ever since then.
I know how, err, shall i say RAVAGED, i got by a certain few of you. As much as i can recall by the way - glimpes in minds eye, & the rest without anything in minds eye.
Oh and this whole time i thought that, the kind of women i found attractive was just my own taste; only i realized it was because of who the women were that i grew up, err, going on adventures with. 
I never really forgot; due to getting taken advantage of, i tried to convince myself it was wrong and never happened; but deep down i knew it was their control & fine; so i "held on" to the truth in my own way, as i came to learn to do throughout life in general from then on; i kept it a secret in a very effective way; knowing how perceptive some can be; i learn to stop trying to decieve, but hide; so id hide the truth, not from others, but from myself. Mistakenly taking it too far, being so young, can you blame myself? And so they stopped being a deep holding on by acting as though im just imagining that those are the events that took place in the past; and started believing that, well, it was all just imagination. But can you really fantasise about a different past? You can long for one sure, but fantasy is about the future. And i felt no longing. It felt like fantasies. Indeed they informed later fantasies too.

Mantras, to repeat a bunch of times amidst meditation or throughout the day, but not too much i think.

-For the transmutation of ones darkness into light; or, the truest internal alchemy. "Ah, lightless place of me, well may I feel it (pause until have feelings of a darker/less-safe world). Indeed, I be. I quest from place then BE (pause until world doesn't seem so dark/unsafe)." Rest a moment.

-For freely living with us.
"Following only propositions that agree with my ownership of my spirit".
